        "description":"Developed an AI-driven financial automation platform for Booke AI, enabling users to streamline bookkeeping processes and improve data accuracy across accounting workflows.Built a high-performance backend using Node.js, Express.js, and Python with TypeScript, delivering scalable RESTful APIs to support real-time data processing and integrations. Designed efficient data handling and optimized database interactions, improving API response times and overall system reliability.The platform automates key financial operations such as transaction categorization, reconciliation, and data matching, reducing manual effort while ensuring accuracy. Implemented structured data processing logic to handle complex financial datasets and support consistent, reliable outputs for end users.Developed a responsive Next.js frontend that provides an intuitive interface for managing and reviewing financial data, ensuring seamless interaction with backend services and an enhanced user experience.",
